Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tasks.model.tasks

Class AbstractTaskList

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tasks.model.tasks.AbstractTaskList
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActiveTaskList, TaskList
    public abstract class AbstractTaskList
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class at the top of hierarchy for task lists. The AbstractTaskList knows a task list's name, ISwapList of Tasks, and the number of completed tasks
    Author:
    Jake Donovan
